<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>User Activation</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background: #f7f7f7; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        .container { max-width: 500px; margin: 40px auto; background: #fff; padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);}
        .otp { font-size: 2em; color: #2d8cf0; letter-spacing: 8px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .footer { color: #888; font-size: 0.9em; margin-top: 30px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Activate Your Account</h2>
        <p>Hello <%= userName %>,</p>
        <p>Thank you for registering with us! To activate your account, please use the following OTP:</p>
        <div class="otp"><%= otp %></div>
        <p>This OTP is valid for <%= otpExpiryMinutes %> minutes.</p>
        <p>If you did not request this, please ignore this email.</p>
        <div class="footer">
            &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Multi-Vendor eCommerce. All rights reserved.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>